digging from both ends.

43
00:02:13,849 --> 00:02:15,819
And when Taiwan’s Minister Chen Min-tong,

44
00:02:15,819 --> 00:02:20,080
who’s responsible for relations between
Taiwan and the mainland,

45
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:23,770
got wind that the plans for the tunnel were
ready and the CCP

46
00:02:23,770 --> 00:02:25,540
was anxious to break ground,

47
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:28,000
he immediately denounced the project,

48
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,650
saying “The proposal is part of China's
consistent

49
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:34,569
