53
00:02:43,530 --> 00:02:45,040
But from the Communist Party’s perspective,

54
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,790
an agreement isn’t really necessary—

55
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:50,049
although it would make things go much smoother.

56
00:02:50,049 --> 00:02:52,340
That’s because the Party considers Taiwan

57
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:55,670
a province of the People’s Republic of China,

58
00:02:55,670 --> 00:02:58,640
and has vowed to seize control of it sooner
or later,

59
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,790
by force if necessary.

60
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:03,260
Actually Chinese president Xi Jinping has
ordered

61
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:05,520
the People’s Liberation Army to be ready

62
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:08,950
for an invasion of Taiwan by 2020.

63
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:13,569
No wonder Taiwan is a bit suspicious of this
underwater tunnel.

64
00:03:13,569 --> 00:03:17,430
The Taiwanese minister also said that by proposing
the tunnel,

65
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:21,280
China was “attacking Taiwan’s potential
for international space

66
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:25,310
using militaristic intimidation and trying
to mislead the public

67
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:29,069
